  "informal_statement": "For every natural number n, the sum of the first n positive even numbers 2 + 4 + ... + 2n equals n * (n + 1).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Induction on n: peel the last term 2(k+1) with Finset.sum_range_succ, apply the hypothesis, and k*(k+1) + 2*(k+1) = (k+1)*(k+2) by ring.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem sum_evens (n : ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range n, (2 * i + 2)) = n * (n + 1)",
